          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and we’re asking everyone to keep an eye out for them. The trucks are a red 1986 K10 Chevy Silverado 4×4 with a short bed, Fleetside, 8cyl engine; black 1987 R10 Chevy Silverado 2×4 short bed, Fleetside, 8cyl engine; and a black 1990 C-1500 Chevy SS, 454 Litter Engine 2×4, the 49th or 50th SS made.",
